Interface MainController<T extends MainController<T>>

  • Type Parameters:
    T -
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DriverBaseController, SeleniumController, WebDriverController

    public interface MainController<T extends MainController<T>>
    This interface is for all methods used by webdriver to interact with app UI
    Author:
    Giannis Papadakis(mailTo:gpapadakis84@gmail.com)
